ViewObject.Name: MnjMfgPrecostingHView
ViewObject.SQLQuery:
SELECT MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_ID, MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_NO, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ORDER_PROJECTION_NO, MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID, MnjMfgPrecostingH.DROP_PERIOD, MnjMfgPrecostingH.BRAND, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NAME, ( SELECT DECODE(StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS,'Style Name',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME,'Style Number',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NAME --'3408946' AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID --46245 and SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) Current_Style_Name, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO, ( SELECT DECODE(StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS,'Style Name',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME,'Style Number',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID and SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) Current_Style_No,
/** Case clause added by Sakibul Islam on 08-Jan-2020 **/ case when ( SELECT DECODE(StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS,'Style Name',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME,'Style Number',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID and SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) is null
then MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO when ( SELECT DECODE(StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS,'Style Name',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME,'Style Number',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID and SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 ) is not null
then ( SELECT DECODE(StyleLineEO.TRACK_BASIS,'Style Name',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NAME,'Style Number',StyleLineEO.STYLE_NUMBER) FROM PWC_MFG_BSS_STYLE_L StyleLineEO, pwc_mfg_bss_buyer_h pwcmfgbssbuyerh, PWC_MFG_BSS_SEASON_D SeasonDetailEO WHERE StyleLineEO.STYLE_IDENTIFIER = MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NO AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.BUYER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.BUYER_ID and SeasonDetailEO.SEASON_NAME = MnjMfgPrecostingH.season --added by Sakibul Islam on 13-Jan-2020 --AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.ORG_ID = mmoda.final_mfg_org_id AND StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID = pwcmfgbssbuyerh.HEADER_ID AND SeasonDetailEO.LINE_ID = StyleLineEO.LINE_ID AND pwcmfgbssbuyerh.header_id = StyleLineEO.HEADER_ID -- added by nahian on 15-apr-18 )
end Conditional_Prod_Style_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.FIT, MnjMfgPrecostingH.END_USER, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ITEM_DESCRIPTION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COLOUR_WASH, MnjMfgPrecostingH.OTHER_CHARGES, MnjMfgPrecostingH.LAB_TEST_CHARGES, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PRINT, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COMMISSION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.SMS_QTY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ORDER_QTY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.COSTING_MOU, MnjMfgPrecostingH.FABRIC_FINANCE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRIM_FINANCE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.WASH_FINANCE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PRODUCTION_UNIT, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CM_MERCHANDISER, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CREATED_BY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.LAST_UPDATED_BY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CREATION_DATE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.LAST_UPDATED_DATE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PROD_PER_LINE_PER_H, MnjMfgPrecostingH.SEASON, MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRANSFER_STATUS, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Status, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Gm_Approval, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Md_Approval, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Cm_Merchandiser_d, MnjMfgPrecostingH.AGENCY_COMMISSION, (select customer_name from ar_customers ac where ac.CUSTOMER_ID = MnjMfgPrecostingH.Buyer_Id) buyer, NULL BUYER_CRITERIA, decode(MnjMfgPrecostingH.Gm_Approval, 'I', 'Inprocess', 'Y', 'Approved', 'Incomplete') gm_status, decode(MnjMfgPrecostingH.Md_Approval, 'I', 'Inprocess', 'Y', 'Approved', 'Incomplete') md_status, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Sample_Doc_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Version_Date, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Version_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Poc_Type, MnjMfgPrecostingH.Prod_Style_No, MnjMfgPrecostingH.PROD_COST_LINE_PER_H, MnjMfgPrecostingH.BPO_QTY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.TOTAL_BPO_TBA_QTY, MnjMfgPrecostingH.CM_CALCULATION, --(select count(1) from MNJ_FILE_UPD_DWN ff -- where ff.file_id = 'PC' || MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_NO) ATTACHEMNT,Commented by Sakibul Islam on 12-Jan-2020 MnjMfgPrecostingH.DIVISION, MnjMfgPrecostingH.ITEM_PURCHASE_TYPE, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_TRACKING, MnjMfgPrecostingH.STYLE_NAME_NEW
FROM MNJ_MFG_PRECOSTING_H MnjMfgPrecostingH where MnjMfgPrecostingH.Buyer_Id in (select V.BUYER_ID from MNJ_USER_WISE_BUYERS_DET_V v where V.USER_ID = :p_userId) and (MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRANSFER_STATUS <> 'N' or MnjMfgPrecostingH.TRANSFER_STATUS is null)
-- order by MnjMfgPrecostingH.Header_Id desc order by TO_NUMBER( MnjMfgPrecostingH.HEADER_NO) desc ,TO_NUMBER(MnjMfgPrecostingH.Version_No) desc
